name: Universe #256 x SubtleGraces
description: Universe #256 x SubtleGraces - Wiran was a universe that was about to implode. 256 was a data stream that traveled in the void and saw it suffer. It saw the only way to stop it from happening was to save the universe to the data stream. It exploded at the moment of connection and disturbed the whole data stream. Now they travel through the void together as a glitchy datastream forever
